  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>This Wonders of Iceland full circle tour is perfect for those who want to experience all the nature, culture and history that this amazing country has to offer. Complete with whale watching, boat trips, geysers, hot springs, two national parks and volcanoes this </span><a data-udi="umb://document/034b02ad431f4de8b15f328605d821cb" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/iceland" title="Iceland">Iceland holiday</a><span> is sure to tick a lot of boxes.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: 20</strong></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/wonders-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
